Bounded on the NW. and N. along lines 1-2-3-4-5-6-7, by Lot 810, La Carlota Psd.; on the N. and NE., along lines 7-8-9-10-11-12, by Najalin River; on the E., along lines 12-13-14, by Lot 1170-B of the subdivision plan; on the S., along line 14-15, by Road; and on the W., long line 15-1, by Lo 810, La Carlota Cadastre.

